OL,3,CBeef industry faces 'perfect storm' as
OL,4,Cprices plunge and costs soar
OL,6,FThe Ulster Farmers' Union is warning
OL,7,Fthat Northern Ireland's beef industry
OL,8,Fis facing a "perfect storm", as it
OL,9,Fsays factory prices continue to spiral
OL,10,Fdownwards, imports surge and
OL,11,Fconfidence across the sector
OL,12,Fdeteriorates.
OL,14,FThe Deputy President of the union says
OL,15,Fthat many farmers now fear prices
OL,16,Fcould soon crash, just months after
OL,17,F"record highs" finally delivered some
OL,18,Fhope back into the sector.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
