OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778691956
OL,3,CBeef industry faces 'perfect storm' as
OL,4,Cprices plunge and costs soar
OL,6,FFarmer Brendan Kelly told UTV: "Our
OL,7,Fbeef price has fallen 65, 70 pence per
OL,8,Fkilo.
OL,10,F"Consumers are on a credit crunch at
OL,11,Fthis particular stage. So yes, they're
OL,12,Ffeeling the pinch as well, but we seem
OL,13,Fto be the ones that are suffering the
OL,14,Floss because it comes straight back to
OL,15,Four bottom line."
OL,17,FDeputy president of the union says
OL,18,Ffarmers are feeling the pinch for
OL,19,Fseveral reasons.
OL,26,@wD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778691956
OL,3,CBeef industry faces 'perfect storm' as
OL,4,Cprices plunge and costs soar
OL,6,FClement Lynch, Ulster Farmers' Union
OL,7,Fsaid: "We have seen rising numbers of
OL,8,Fimports coming in.
OL,10,F"A month ago, abattoirs or meat plants
OL,11,Fwere looking for cattle and were very
OL,12,Fanxious to get cattle.
OL,14,F"Over the last couple of weeks, we see
OL,15,Ffarmers waiting up to four weeks to
OL,16,Fget cattle slaughtered.
OL,18,F"And within those four weeks, the
OL,19,Fprices have dropped on a weekly basis."
OL,26,@{D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778691956
OL,3,CBeef industry faces 'perfect storm' as
OL,4,Cprices plunge and costs soar
OL,6,FThere is also growing concern that the
OL,7,Fpublic, who are facing rising costs
OL,8,Felsewhere, are moving away from beef
OL,9,Fand towards cheaper meats.
OL,11,FButcher Trevor Barr said: "The
OL,12,Fconsumer is now changing its eating
OL,13,Fhabits.
OL,15,F"They're moving back to pork, they're
OL,16,Fmoving onto chicken, and they're
OL,17,Fmoving onto cheaper cuts because the
OL,18,Fcost of living has got so high.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778691956
OL,3,CBeef industry faces 'perfect storm' as
OL,4,Cprices plunge and costs soar
OL,6,F"If we went back a year and a half
OL,7,Fago, we would maybe sell a couple
OL,8,Fhundred chickens a week.
OL,10,F"Today, we could be selling 400, 450
OL,11,Fchickens a week.
OL,13,F"We've noticed our beef sales have
OL,14,Fmoved down slightly because of the
OL,15,Fprice of beef and the cost of living."
OL,17,FBrendan Kelly says farmers are simply
OL,18,Fcalling for a fairer system.
OL,26,@wD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778691956
OL,3,CBeef industry faces 'perfect storm' as
OL,4,Cprices plunge and costs soar
OL,6,FMr Kelly continued: "We would just
OL,7,Flike fair play. We're price takers. We
OL,8,Fcan't dictate what we get.
OL,10,F"If someone buys a BMW car, BMW
OL,11,Fdictate what price that's sold at. We
OL,12,Fdon't have that luxury.
OL,14,F"We always seem to have to do more for
OL,15,Fless. Succession is really becoming a
OL,16,Fproblem.
OL,18,F"There's no young people wanting to
OL,19,Fcome into this industry and if things
OL,20,Fdon't change, the industry will be
OL,21,Ftotally broken forever."
OL,26,@}D@XO]
